headline: 3 Big Stock Splits Are Right Around the Corner -- and 2 of the 3 Stocks Are Great Picks During Uncertain Markets
summary: Fastenal has a two-for-one stock split coming soon, but its customers appear to be getting nervous about tariffs.  O'Reilly Automotive seems likely to continue its winning ways even if the economy stumbles.  What's something that receives more attention from investors than is probably warranted?

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 to Ignore
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is home to the biggest and most well-known companies in the market, making it a go-to index for investors seeking stability. But not all large-cap stocks are created equal - some are struggling with slowing growth, declining margins, or increased competition.
